The following is a discussion of Kansas City Southern's results of operations, certain changes in its financial position, liquidity, capital structure and business developments for the years ended December 31, 2021 and 2020. This discussion should be read in conjunction with the included consolidated financial statements, the related notes, and other information included in this report.
